Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/DBusBindings

Package: libdbus-glib
Section: admin
Priority: required
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: dbus-glib (= ${binary:Version})
Description: provides GLib interface functions to the D-Bus API
 D-Bus is a message bus system, a simple way for applications 
 to talk to one another. 
 .
 This package provides libdbus-glib-1, a shared library which
 provides GLib interface functions to the D-Bus API.
 
Package: libdbus-glib-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Provides: dbus-glib-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Depends: libdbus-glib (= ${binary:Version}), dbus-dev, 
 libexpat-dev, glib2-dev
Description: Development headers and static libraries for D-Bus
 This package provides the D-Bus static library, pkgconfig data 
 and header files required for developing applications which use 
 the GLib D-Bus API.

Package: dbus-glib-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Recommends: vim
Depends: libdbus-glib (= ${binary:Version})
Description: documentation for D-Bus GLib userspace tools
 This package provides man pages for D-Bus GLib userspace tools.
